# Global Lending Risk & Repayment Performance Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes international lending data to identify repayment performance, financial exposure, outstanding balances, and country-level risk trends.

The goal was to transform raw financial records into actionable business insights using SQL and Power BI.

## Business Questions

* Which countries received the highest loan disbursements?
* Where are repayment risks increasing?
* Which loans have high outstanding balances?
* How does repayment performance vary across regions?

## Tools Used

* SQL (data cleaning, KPI logic, views, risk segmentation)
* Power BI (interactive dashboard, DAX, storytelling)
* Excel / CSV data preparation

## Dashboard Features

* Total Disbursed
* Total Repaid
* Outstanding Amount
* Repayment Rate %
* Country Risk Comparison
* Time Trends
* Loan Status Distribution

## Key Insights

* Certain countries hold significantly higher outstanding balances.
* Repayment rates vary widely across regions.
* A subset of loans drives most exposure risk.

## Files Included

* SQL scripts
* Power BI dashboard
* Screenshots

